{"storyMeta":{"storyReviewType":"NONE","storyId":"main_8_level_st_08-01","storyGroup":"main_8","storySort":3,"storyDependence":"main_8_level_main_08-01_end","storyCanShow":0,"storyCode":"M8-1","storyName":"今日，血色满溢","storyPic":null,"storyInfo":"切尔诺伯格核心城，中央区，萨卡兹雇佣兵对整合运动感染者举起屠刀。而阿米娅与迷迭香，带领着队伍坚定地前进着。","storyCanEnter":1,"storyTxt":"obt/main/level_st_08-01","avgTag":"幕间","unLockType":"STAGE_CLEAR","costItemType":"NONE","costItemId":null,"costItemCount":0,"stageCount":1,"requiredStages":[{"stageId":"st_08-01","minState":"PLAYED","maxState":"COMPLETE"}],"prev":1,"next":3,"characters":["整合运动感染者","迷迭香小队成员","迷迭香","萨卡兹雇佣兵","阿米娅","罗德岛干员","凯尔希","牧群化萨卡兹战士"]},"lines":[{"type":"header","key":"title_test","skippable":"true","mode":"BLACK_MASK","text":"","id":0},{"type":"stopmusic","id":1},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":2},{"type":"dialog","id":3},{"type":"character","id":4},{"type":"playmusic","intro":"$loneliness_intro","key":"https://static.prts.wiki/music/music/static/m_avg/m_avg_loneliness_loop.mp3","volume":"0.8","crossfade":"1.5","id":5,"musicid":0},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":6},{"type":"character","id":7},{"type":"background","image":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/b/ba/Avg_bg_bg_cher_0.png","screenadapt":"coverall","id":8},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":9},{"type":"text","text":"法律，原始的法律，同态复仇的背后是同样原始的需要，对暴力的需要。","id":10},{"type":"text","text":"城邦向居民许诺，用优厚的生活与稳定的环境安抚他们——","id":11},{"type":"text","text":"让他们的生命服务于一个人造的目标，驯化他们天性中的征服意志，教他们安心，令他们软弱。","id":12},{"type":"text","text":"我们的陛下是睿智的。","id":13},{"type":"text","text":"诸多城邦将有力视作罪恶，将匮乏勇气当作美德，将畏惧死亡看作进步。陛下将撕去他们的遮羞布，让他们思考，让他们反省。","id":14},{"type":"text","text":"我们人类的血脉里，一直流淌着一种渴望，一种对以行为宣泄自身生命力量的渴望。","id":15},{"type":"dialog","id":16},{"type":"character","id":17},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":18},{"type":"background","image":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/b/bb/Avg_bg_bg_cher_9.png","screenadapt":"coverall","id":19},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":20},{"type":"text","text":"公平不是天生的。公平是依赖有智慧、有意志的力量去缔造的。","id":21},{"type":"text","text":"陛下将把他们需要的这一切，被城市带走的这一切，还给他们。","id":22},{"type":"text","text":"新的目标将被宣布，陛下会重整他们被日常生活与无聊磨平的思维，唤醒他们身体里被僵化的伦理束缚多时的血性。","id":23},{"type":"text","text":"暴力贯穿我们的躯体，如果我们不让它在我们的身心中自然发芽，我们将变得怨毒、渺小而麻木，也将因此招致自我的毁灭。","id":24},{"type":"text","text":"常时畏惧的人是可鄙的。","id":25},{"type":"text","text":"一个人想要活着，就应当被浸没在暴力之中，认清众多道德的虚伪，知晓现下大地的贫瘠。","id":26},{"type":"text","text":"只有暴力才是真实的，能被感触的。","id":27},{"type":"dialog","id":28},{"type":"character","id":29},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":30},{"type":"background","image":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/c/c7/Avg_bg_bg_cher_6.png","screenadapt":"coverall","id":31},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":32},{"type":"text","text":"不是惩罚，不是统治，不是价值的衡量与怀柔的伪饰，我们用拳头和武器告诉他们我们活着，且应当活着。只有活着的人才该活着。","id":33},{"type":"text","text":"我不责怪皇帝陛下对我判下的处罚，我不识时务地侮蔑了他向民众倾诉的仁慈话语，因他舍不得他的子民轻易遭受剧烈转变的痛楚。","id":34},{"type":"text","text":"就算这样，我对真理的坦述也不得停止。我必须不断地、不断地赞美陛下的真知灼见，我只能呼唤我的诚实，我不能沉默。","id":35},{"type":"text","text":"事实上，我们不想要所谓正义，也不企盼安宁。","id":36},{"type":"dialog","id":37},{"type":"character","id":38},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":39},{"type":"background","image":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/f/f0/Avg_bg_bg_perimeter.png","screenadapt":"coverall","id":40},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":41},{"type":"text","text":"目光短浅、奔走于自身利益的人才会沉湎于安宁。","id":42},{"type":"text","text":"我们想要的，是动用我们血管里奔涌的暴力，我们这自文明起源处就被启发了的天性，我们奋勇挣扎和胜利的源泉。我们要使用暴力。","id":43},{"type":"text","text":"一切修饰都只是正当化我们的需求，但这无关紧要。","id":44},{"type":"text","text":"当我们需要，我们就当直接索求，把修饰留给历史学家和道德卫士吧，他们才需要正当性，我们的生存可比任何理论都更正当。","id":45},{"type":"text","text":"我们要伤害人，战胜人，毁灭人，如果这对乌萨斯是场灾难，那我们就应该把灾难带给他人，带给乌萨斯之外的人。","id":46},{"type":"text","text":"如果他们不强健，他们就该被消灭，有的人比其他人更适合生存，也更适合成就。","id":47},{"type":"text","text":"软弱就是邪恶。强大就是崇高。我们的法律理当建立在健全市民的身心需求之上，我们的国家不该服务于蛆虫，也不该喂养更多病患。","id":48},{"type":"text","text":"愿我所鄙夷的这些狭隘的、贪图安逸的臣民在审判后永居血湖，愿陛下带领乌萨斯走向永远的繁荣。","id":49},{"type":"dialog","id":50},{"type":"character","id":51},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":52},{"type":"text","text":"——异端的君主传道士在被乌萨斯皇帝判处绞刑后，走上绞架前的最后一次布道。","id":53},{"type":"dialog","id":54},{"type":"stopmusic","crossfade":"2","id":55},{"type":"background","image":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/d/df/Avg_bg_bg_chercen_2.png","screenadapt":"coverall","id":56},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":57},{"type":"text","text":"切尔诺伯格核心城，中央区","id":58},{"type":"playmusic","intro":"$nervous_intro","key":"https://static.prts.wiki/music/music/act9d0d0/m_avg_nervous_loop.mp3","volume":"0.4","id":59,"musicid":1},{"type":"character","name":"char_1002_nsabr_2","id":60},{"type":"dialogue","name":"整合运动感染者","text":"间谍！乌萨斯的间谍！","id":61,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/2/27/Avg_char_1002_nsabr_2.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"整合运动感染者","text":"他们在这！去和大伙说，他们在这！","id":62,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/2/27/Avg_char_1002_nsabr_2.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"整合运动感染者","text":"杀了他们，杀了他们！把他们挂在对接层上，把他们碾在龙门的楼上！","id":63,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/2/27/Avg_char_1002_nsabr_2.png"},{"type":"character","id":64},{"type":"dialogue","name":"迷迭香小队成员","text":"后撤吧，迷迭香。他们占据了整座商厦，这个街区已经被他们封锁了。","id":65},{"type":"dialogue","name":"迷迭香小队成员","text":"迷迭香......！","id":66},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_042","id":67},{"type":"dialogue","name":"迷迭香","text":"我来吧。绕远路的话，我们会被其它地方的整合运动攻击的。","id":68,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/6/6a/Avg_avg_npc_042.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":69},{"type":"character","id":70},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":71},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":72},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_053","id":73},{"type":"dialogue","name":"萨卡兹雇佣兵","text":"——","id":74,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/f/f5/Avg_avg_npc_053.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":75},{"type":"character","id":76},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":77},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":78},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_042","id":79},{"type":"dialogue","name":"迷迭香","text":"萨卡兹......","id":80,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/6/6a/Avg_avg_npc_042.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":81},{"type":"character","id":82},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":83},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":84},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_053","id":85},{"type":"dialogue","name":"萨卡兹雇佣兵","text":"喂，你，看着点，那个术师......看着点！别让她动手！","id":86,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/f/f5/Avg_avg_npc_053.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"萨卡兹雇佣兵","text":"把她们弄死！快点！","id":87,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/f/f5/Avg_avg_npc_053.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_1002_nsabr_2","id":88},{"type":"dialogue","name":"整合运动感染者","text":"好！好！！杀呀，杀了他们！","id":89,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/2/27/Avg_char_1002_nsabr_2.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":90},{"type":"character","id":91},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_gen_walk_n","id":92},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_042","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":93},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":94},{"type":"dialogue","name":"迷迭香","text":"（哥伦比亚语）要杀我吗？","id":95,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/6/6a/Avg_avg_npc_042.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_1002_nsabr_2","id":96},{"type":"dialogue","name":"整合运动感染者","text":"叫你们不知好歹，叫你们脖子上拴的是乌萨斯的链子！","id":97,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/2/27/Avg_char_1002_nsabr_2.png"},{"type":"character","id":98},{"type":"dialogue","name":"迷迭香小队成员","text":"迷迭香，不值得！他们已经差不多疯了！我们换个街区，找找另外的突破口！","id":99},{"type":"character","name":"char_1002_nsabr_2","id":100},{"type":"dialogue","name":"整合运动感染者","text":"拿弩枪来！拿弩枪来......把她的头，把她的头给打爆！刚才来这里的那只兔子也是......你也是！","id":101,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/2/27/Avg_char_1002_nsabr_2.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_042","id":102},{"type":"dialogue","name":"迷迭香","text":"阿米娅没从这里走，是因为她不想像我这么做。","id":103,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/6/6a/Avg_avg_npc_042.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_1002_nsabr_2","id":104},{"type":"dialogue","name":"整合运动感染者","text":"你们用什么眼神看我？你是感染者，你是感染者，你们怎么用那种眼神看我？！","id":105,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/2/27/Avg_char_1002_nsabr_2.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"整合运动感染者","text":"合作？生还？什么东西，哈哈，说什么，乌萨斯都战胜不了我们，我们赢了，赢了！","id":106,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/2/27/Avg_char_1002_nsabr_2.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"整合运动感染者","text":"射击！打她呀，打她！","id":107,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/2/27/Avg_char_1002_nsabr_2.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_042","id":108},{"type":"dialogue","name":"迷迭香","text":"没用的。","id":109,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/6/6a/Avg_avg_npc_042.png"},{"type":"character","id":110},{"type":"dialog","id":111},{"type":"blocker","a":"0.7","r":"0.95","g":"0.95","b":"0.95","fadetime":"0.02","block":"true","id":112},{"type":"playsound","key":"$e_atk_arrow_h","id":113},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0.95","g":"0.95","b":"0.95","fadetime":"0.25","block":"true","id":114},{"type":"camerashake","duration":"0.6","xstrength":"5","ystrength":"8","vibrato":"30","randomness":"90","block":"true","id":115},{"type":"blocker","a":"0.7","r":"0.95","g":"0.95","b":"0.95","fadetime":"0.02","block":"true","id":116},{"type":"playsound","key":"$e_atk_arrow_h","id":117},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0.95","g":"0.95","b":"0.95","fadetime":"0.25","block":"true","id":118},{"type":"camerashake","duration":"0.6","xstrength":"5","ystrength":"8","vibrato":"30","randomness":"90","block":"true","id":119},{"type":"delay","time":"0.5","id":120},{"type":"dialog","id":121},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"1","g":"1","b":"1","afrom":"0","rfrom":"0","gfrom":"0","bfrom":"0","fadetime":"0.1","block":"true","id":122},{"type":"playsound","key":"$e_skill_skulsrsword","volume":"0.9","id":123},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","fadetime":"1.5","block":"false","id":124},{"type":"camerashake","duration":"0.5","xstrength":"10","ystrength":"12","vibrato":"30","randomness":"90","fadeout":"true","block":"true","id":125},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_sp_ballista","id":126},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0.25","block":"true","id":127},{"type":"delay","time":"2","id":128},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_042","id":129},{"type":"dialogue","name":"迷迭香","text":"没用的。我不想你伤到我，你就什么都做不到。","id":130,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/6/6a/Avg_avg_npc_042.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_1002_nsabr_2","id":131},{"type":"dialogue","name":"整合运动感染者","text":"怎么回事......怎么回事！继续打！继续打！全部轰上去！","id":132,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/2/27/Avg_char_1002_nsabr_2.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"整合运动感染者","text":"那是墙吗？什么法术......什么东西！弩箭撞上去都烂了，都烂了！","id":133,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/2/27/Avg_char_1002_nsabr_2.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_053","id":134},{"type":"dialogue","name":"萨卡兹雇佣兵","text":"别打那几个墙壁似的东西，没有用！那个看着就很坚固！叫术师们来！","id":135,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/f/f5/Avg_avg_npc_053.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_1002_nsabr_2","id":136},{"type":"dialogue","name":"整合运动感染者","text":"你懂什么，我们就是对着她的脸打的！","id":137,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/2/27/Avg_char_1002_nsabr_2.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"整合运动感染者","text":"但是箭射到她身上，碎片弹打到她脸上之前，就都撞上了什么东西，透明的墙还是什么，什么东西！碎了，进不去！","id":138,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/2/27/Avg_char_1002_nsabr_2.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"整合运动感染者","text":"垃圾术师，看你撑到什么时候......你还有多少体力？！你撑不了多久，看你撑到什么时候！","id":139,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/2/27/Avg_char_1002_nsabr_2.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"整合运动感染者","text":"为什么，为什么......你们难道射不穿吗，她什么也没做啊，你们的弩炮呢，你们的赋能弩箭呢！","id":140,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/2/27/Avg_char_1002_nsabr_2.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"整合运动感染者","text":"轰炸啊，把她炸开花，炸得粉碎，炸得和该死的乌萨斯人一样，然后做成晚上的汤！","id":141,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/2/27/Avg_char_1002_nsabr_2.png"},{"type":"character","id":142},{"type":"dialogue","name":"迷迭香小队成员","text":"这里是迷迭香小队，阿米娅！接通你了......劝劝她，你劝劝她！","id":143},{"type":"dialogue","name":"迷迭香小队成员","text":"迷迭香，听通讯！","id":144},{"type":"character","name":"char_1002_nsabr_2","id":145},{"type":"dialogue","name":"整合运动感染者","text":"穿制服的，啊哈，穿制服的，我们把你们吊死，风干在电线上，让腐毛嘴把你们啄个稀烂。","id":146,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/2/27/Avg_char_1002_nsabr_2.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"整合运动感染者","text":"让你们知道，知道看不起我们的下场！","id":147,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/2/27/Avg_char_1002_nsabr_2.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"整合运动感染者","text":"看不起我们的，害我们的，以前给我们使脸色的，哈哈，呵，全都杀了。","id":148,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/2/27/Avg_char_1002_nsabr_2.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"整合运动感染者","text":"全都丢进引擎里，突突突突突突，肉沫喷出来，哈哈哈哈哈......！","id":149,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/2/27/Avg_char_1002_nsabr_2.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_053","id":150},{"type":"dialogue","name":"萨卡兹雇佣兵","text":"你在干什么？你怎么在这手舞足蹈？！不要暴露小队位置！","id":151,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/f/f5/Avg_avg_npc_053.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_1002_nsabr_2","id":152},{"type":"dialogue","name":"整合运动感染者","text":"废话这么多......魔族玩意！硬角的畜生！你凭什么命令我？","id":153,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/2/27/Avg_char_1002_nsabr_2.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"整合运动感染者","text":"你当你是塔露拉，还是那个好死不死的老畜生？完了，他已经完蛋了！砰！","id":154,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/2/27/Avg_char_1002_nsabr_2.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"整合运动感染者","text":"你们都得完蛋！我们乌萨斯人感染者......杀！杀了你们所有人！你们都是——","id":155,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/2/27/Avg_char_1002_nsabr_2.png"},{"type":"character","id":156},{"type":"dialog","id":157},{"type":"playsound","key":"$fightgeneral","text":"","id":158},{"type":"camerashake","duration":"1","xstrength":"10","ystrength":"12","vibrato":"30","randomness":"90","fadeout":"true","block":"true","id":159},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":160},{"type":"text","text":"萨卡兹将感染者踢下了窗口。","id":161},{"type":"text","text":"感染者嚎叫着，或者说，笑着，从七楼摔落在地，紧接着被弩炮炸成了碎片。","id":162},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_053","id":163},{"type":"dialogue","name":"萨卡兹雇佣兵","text":"啐。","id":164,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/f/f5/Avg_avg_npc_053.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"萨卡兹雇佣兵","text":"动手。把重火力武器拿出来。宰了他们。","id":165,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/f/f5/Avg_avg_npc_053.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_042","id":166},{"type":"dialogue","name":"迷迭香","text":"阿米娅，听得见吗？就从说好的路线走。通话完毕。","id":167,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/6/6a/Avg_avg_npc_042.png"},{"type":"character","id":168},{"type":"dialogue","name":"迷迭香小队成员","text":"迷迭香......","id":169},{"type":"dialog","id":170},{"type":"character","id":171},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":172},{"type":"background","image":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/d/df/Avg_bg_bg_chercen_2.png","screenadapt":"coverall","id":173},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":174},{"type":"character","name":"char_002_amiya_1#7","id":175},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿米娅","text":"游击队现在的动向呢？","id":176,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/a/ad/Avg_char_002_amiya_7.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_012","id":177},{"type":"dialogue","name":"罗德岛干员","text":"侦查干员汇报说，已经集合的游击队正在中央大道上正面攻击其他整合运动守军。","id":178,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/1/1b/Avg_avg_npc_012.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"罗德岛干员","text":"还有一些游击队的小队，不进反退，他们四散向城市的各个部分......","id":179,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/1/1b/Avg_avg_npc_012.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_002_amiya_1#7","name2":"avg_npc_012","focus":"1","id":180},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿米娅","text":"......是这样的，游击队还有其他的职责。","id":181,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/a/ad/Avg_char_002_amiya_7.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿米娅","text":"但我们这两支小队已经无暇顾及核心城内其他部分的状况了。","id":182,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/a/ad/Avg_char_002_amiya_7.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿米娅","text":"突破封锁需要的时间越长，我们剩下的时间就越少。","id":183,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/a/ad/Avg_char_002_amiya_7.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿米娅","text":"如果其他反游击队派的感染者被游击队牵制住了，我们就能更快到达指挥塔。不能浪费这个机会。","id":184,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/a/ad/Avg_char_002_amiya_7.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿米娅","text":"对整个局势的控制，依赖Raidian和Mantra的判断。对战场的控制......","id":185,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/a/ad/Avg_char_002_amiya_7.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿米娅","text":"......我和迷迭香都需要更多思考的空间。","id":186,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/a/ad/Avg_char_002_amiya_7.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_002_amiya_1#7","name2":"avg_npc_012","focus":"2","id":187},{"type":"dialogue","name":"罗德岛干员","text":"所以，迷迭香......","id":188,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/1/1b/Avg_avg_npc_012.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_002_amiya_1#7","name2":"avg_npc_012","focus":"1","id":189},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿米娅","text":"在我们排除了伏击干扰后，其他的迂回路线也得到了保证。但迷迭香，我想，迷迭香大概只会选择破除眼前的阻碍吧。","id":190,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/a/ad/Avg_char_002_amiya_7.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿米娅","text":"她大概已经这么做了。","id":191,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/a/ad/Avg_char_002_amiya_7.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_002_amiya_1#7","name2":"avg_npc_012","focus":"2","id":192},{"type":"dialogue","name":"罗德岛干员","text":"......哎。","id":193,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/1/1b/Avg_avg_npc_012.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"罗德岛干员","text":"凯尔希医生说中了。真是一塌糊涂。","id":194,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/1/1b/Avg_avg_npc_012.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"罗德岛干员","text":"整合运动已经崩溃了，他们的自相残杀比对游击队的攻击来得还快。","id":195,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/1/1b/Avg_avg_npc_012.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"罗德岛干员","text":"平常他们自己的摩擦肯定也很多，现在爱国者死了，这个消息一下子被点爆了，然后什么都乱掉了。","id":196,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/1/1b/Avg_avg_npc_012.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"罗德岛干员","text":"看看一路上那种惨状，我不信他们能有多团结。","id":197,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/1/1b/Avg_avg_npc_012.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_002_amiya_1#7","name2":"avg_npc_012","focus":"1","id":198},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿米娅","text":"......","id":199,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/a/ad/Avg_char_002_amiya_7.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿米娅","text":"通知其他小队成员，集合。让术师们收回无人机。我们去和迷迭香汇合。","id":200,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/a/ad/Avg_char_002_amiya_7.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":201},{"type":"character","id":202},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":203},{"type":"background","image":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/d/df/Avg_bg_bg_chercen_2.png","screenadapt":"coverall","id":204},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":205},{"type":"character","name":"char_002_amiya_1","name2":"avg_npc_042","focus":"2","id":206},{"type":"dialogue","name":"迷迭香","text":"啊，阿米娅。","id":207,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/6/6a/Avg_avg_npc_042.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"迷迭香","text":"这里已经处理好了。","id":208,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/6/6a/Avg_avg_npc_042.png"},{"type":"character","id":209},{"type":"dialogue","name":"迷迭香小队成员","text":"......我们......","id":210},{"type":"dialogue","name":"迷迭香小队成员","text":"对不起，阿米娅。我们该有更好的处理方式的。","id":211},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_042","id":212},{"type":"dialogue","name":"迷迭香","text":"是我要这么做的。","id":213,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/6/6a/Avg_avg_npc_042.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"迷迭香","text":"交涉失败不是问题，他们那个样子，是没法交流的。","id":214,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/6/6a/Avg_avg_npc_042.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"迷迭香","text":"可是他们在做坏事，放任他们，只会发生更多坏事。","id":215,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/6/6a/Avg_avg_npc_042.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_012","id":216},{"type":"dialogue","name":"罗德岛干员","text":"整栋楼都......整栋楼你都......","id":217,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/1/1b/Avg_avg_npc_012.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_042","name2":"avg_npc_012","focus":"1","id":218},{"type":"dialogue","name":"迷迭香","text":"我做得太过火了吗？","id":219,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/6/6a/Avg_avg_npc_042.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_042","name2":"avg_npc_012","focus":"2","id":220},{"type":"dialogue","name":"罗德岛干员","text":"没有，没有。不，只是我没和你一起出过任务。亲眼看见，很震撼。","id":221,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/1/1b/Avg_avg_npc_012.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"罗德岛干员","text":"不愧是罗德岛的底牌，最强的战争机器......","id":222,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/1/1b/Avg_avg_npc_012.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_042","name2":"avg_npc_012","focus":"1","id":223},{"type":"dialogue","name":"迷迭香","text":"......","id":224,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/6/6a/Avg_avg_npc_042.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_012","id":225},{"type":"dialogue","name":"罗德岛干员","text":"......呃。","id":226,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/1/1b/Avg_avg_npc_012.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"罗德岛干员","text":"（阿米娅，我说错话了？）","id":227,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/1/1b/Avg_avg_npc_012.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_002_amiya_1#4","id":228},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿米娅","text":"......","id":229,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/e/ed/Avg_char_002_amiya_4.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":230},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","initr":"2","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":231},{"type":"background","image":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/e/ef/Avg_bg_bg_bridge.png","screenadapt":"coverall","block":"true","id":232},{"type":"character","fadetime":"0","id":233},{"type":"cameraeffect","effect":"Grayscale","keep":"true","amount":"1","fadetime":"0","id":234},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":235},{"type":"text","text":"核心城行动队离舰前夕","id":236},{"type":"character","name":"char_003_kalts_1","id":237},{"type":"dialogue","name":"凯尔希","text":"我不会允许。","id":238,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/d/d3/Avg_char_003_kalts_1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_003_kalts_1","name2":"char_002_amiya_1#7","focus":"2","id":239},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿米娅","text":"凯尔希医生。这一次，我肯定要这么做的。","id":240,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/a/ad/Avg_char_002_amiya_7.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_003_kalts_1","name2":"char_002_amiya_1#7","focus":"1","id":241},{"type":"dialogue","name":"凯尔希","text":"这个问题我们探讨过很多次了，阿米娅。","id":242,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/d/d3/Avg_char_003_kalts_1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"凯尔希","text":"你的源石技艺耗费的是你的体力，甚至是你新陈代谢所需的生理活性。","id":243,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/d/d3/Avg_char_003_kalts_1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"凯尔希","text":"你的生命在......流逝。你不是一台机器，一门舰炮，你不能更换零件，也不能被继续加工。","id":244,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/d/d3/Avg_char_003_kalts_1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_003_kalts_1","name2":"char_002_amiya_1#7","focus":"2","id":245},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿米娅","text":"我知道。","id":246,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/a/ad/Avg_char_002_amiya_7.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_003_kalts_1","name2":"char_002_amiya_1#7","focus":"1","id":247},{"type":"dialogue","name":"凯尔希","text":"不。也许你还不知道。","id":248,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/d/d3/Avg_char_003_kalts_1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"凯尔希","text":"......又一个太过漫长的记忆。我不确定那会给你的身体带来多大的压力。","id":249,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/d/d3/Avg_char_003_kalts_1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"凯尔希","text":"每一次模拟的结果都很不理想，我还会排除这个选项。","id":250,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/d/d3/Avg_char_003_kalts_1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_003_kalts_1","name2":"char_002_amiya_1#7","focus":"2","id":251},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿米娅","text":"那这样，凯尔希医生，我这么说。","id":252,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/a/ad/Avg_char_002_amiya_7.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿米娅","text":"这一次我必须这么做。我要再解开一枚戒指。","id":253,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/a/ad/Avg_char_002_amiya_7.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_003_kalts_1","name2":"char_002_amiya_1#7","focus":"1","id":254},{"type":"dialogue","name":"凯尔希","text":"阿米娅，我们在探讨一种暴力。这是你对我这么说的。如果你不希望我现在阻止你，当时的你也不会让我立誓。","id":255,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/d/d3/Avg_char_003_kalts_1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"凯尔希","text":"议长与我一同铸造这些戒指，为的就是不让后来者轻易地走上这条道路。","id":256,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/d/d3/Avg_char_003_kalts_1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_003_kalts_1","name2":"char_002_amiya_1#7","focus":"2","id":257},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿米娅","text":"我是在使用它，凯尔希医生。我不会为武器辩护，也绝不会说哪一种能更快杀人的武器是好的。","id":258,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/a/ad/Avg_char_002_amiya_7.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿米娅","text":"但是，特蕾西娅小姐留给我的东西，绝对不一样。","id":259,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/a/ad/Avg_char_002_amiya_7.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿米娅","text":"从最开始起，它也许就不是被当做一种武器设计出来的。","id":260,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/a/ad/Avg_char_002_amiya_7.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿米娅","text":"它不该被用来杀死谁......从来都不是。在使用它时，我在想的是我应该救下谁。","id":261,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/a/ad/Avg_char_002_amiya_7.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿米娅","text":"这是我这几年和它共处得出的结论。","id":262,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/a/ad/Avg_char_002_amiya_7.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_003_kalts_1","name2":"char_002_amiya_1#7","focus":"1","id":263},{"type":"dialogue","name":"凯尔希","text":"......信任一种武器绝非明智之举。","id":264,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/d/d3/Avg_char_003_kalts_1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"凯尔希","text":"如果你要把它当做手术工具而不是凶器去使用，你就得掌控它的刀刃。","id":265,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/d/d3/Avg_char_003_kalts_1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"凯尔希","text":"刀刃对敌我而言都是刀刃，无论你怎么运用，它的性质依然不会改变。","id":266,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/d/d3/Avg_char_003_kalts_1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"凯尔希","text":"阿米娅......它会割伤你。","id":267,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/d/d3/Avg_char_003_kalts_1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_003_kalts_1","name2":"char_002_amiya_1#7","focus":"2","id":268},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿米娅","text":"凯尔希医生，我不怕。","id":269,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/a/ad/Avg_char_002_amiya_7.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿米娅","text":"伤口是会愈合的。","id":270,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/a/ad/Avg_char_002_amiya_7.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_003_kalts_1","name2":"char_002_amiya_1#7","focus":"1","id":271},{"type":"dialogue","name":"凯尔希","text":"可是那会留下疤痕。令人不忍直视的疤痕。","id":272,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/d/d3/Avg_char_003_kalts_1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_003_kalts_1","name2":"char_002_amiya_1#4","focus":"2","id":273},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿米娅","text":"......呜。","id":274,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/e/ed/Avg_char_002_amiya_4.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_003_kalts_1","name2":"char_002_amiya_1#7","focus":"2","id":275},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿米娅","text":"但我......我不会放弃的。","id":276,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/a/ad/Avg_char_002_amiya_7.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿米娅","text":"源石已经让我的身体变成那样了。再多伤口......也只是一两个伤口而已。","id":277,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/a/ad/Avg_char_002_amiya_7.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿米娅","text":"我不是一件武器。","id":278,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/a/ad/Avg_char_002_amiya_7.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_003_kalts_1","name2":"char_002_amiya_1#7","focus":"1","id":279},{"type":"dialogue","name":"凯尔希","text":"需要我再举一次那个伤人的例子吗？","id":280,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/d/d3/Avg_char_003_kalts_1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_003_kalts_1","name2":"char_002_amiya_1#7","focus":"2","id":281},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿米娅","text":"——什么例子？","id":282,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/a/ad/Avg_char_002_amiya_7.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_003_kalts_1","name2":"char_002_amiya_1#7","focus":"1","id":283},{"type":"dialogue","name":"凯尔希","text":"谁来证明你我不是一种武器？","id":284,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/d/d3/Avg_char_003_kalts_1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"凯尔希","text":"我们是否是一种武器，这要谁来定义？","id":285,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/d/d3/Avg_char_003_kalts_1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"凯尔希","text":"武器会思考吗，会思考的武器会更可怕吗，拥有自我意识就不再是一种武器了吗？","id":286,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/d/d3/Avg_char_003_kalts_1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"凯尔希","text":"不，阿米娅。我不同意。","id":287,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/d/d3/Avg_char_003_kalts_1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"凯尔希","text":"虽然我知道——","id":288,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/d/d3/Avg_char_003_kalts_1.png"},{"type":"character","id":289},{"type":"dialog","id":290},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","initr":"2","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":291},{"type":"text","text":"你已经长大了。","id":292},{"type":"text","text":"我阻止不了你。","id":293},{"type":"text","text":"决定是你自己来做。","id":294},{"type":"dialog","id":295},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","initr":"2","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":296},{"type":"background","image":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/d/df/Avg_bg_bg_chercen_2.png","screenadapt":"coverall","id":297},{"type":"character","fadetime":"0","id":298},{"type":"cameraeffect","effect":"Grayscale","keep":"true","amount":"0","fadetime":"0","id":299},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":300},{"type":"character","name":"char_002_amiya_1#4","id":301},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿米娅","text":"......","id":302,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/e/ed/Avg_char_002_amiya_4.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_002_amiya_1","id":303},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿米娅","text":"是的，干员，你说错话了。","id":304,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/0/09/Avg_char_002_amiya_1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿米娅","text":"你见过，嗯......那么......","id":305,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/0/09/Avg_char_002_amiya_1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿米娅","text":"......可爱的......","id":306,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/0/09/Avg_char_002_amiya_1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿米娅","text":"兵器......吗？","id":307,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/0/09/Avg_char_002_amiya_1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿米娅","text":"唔。不，我也不是......","id":308,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/0/09/Avg_char_002_amiya_1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_042","id":309},{"type":"dialogue","name":"迷迭香","text":"阿米娅......更可爱。","id":310,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/6/6a/Avg_avg_npc_042.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_002_amiya_1#5","id":311},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿米娅","text":"对，对不起！我想不出......想不出其他该怎么说......","id":312,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/1/1a/Avg_char_002_amiya_5.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿米娅","text":"我们是人。是有喜怒哀乐的人。","id":313,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/1/1a/Avg_char_002_amiya_5.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿米娅","text":"在这之后，找个机会向她道歉吧。","id":314,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/1/1a/Avg_char_002_amiya_5.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_002_amiya_1#5","name2":"avg_npc_042","focus":"2","id":315},{"type":"dialogue","name":"迷迭香","text":"没有，没有，阿米娅。没事的。","id":316,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/6/6a/Avg_avg_npc_042.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"迷迭香","text":"走吧，我们一起。","id":317,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/6/6a/Avg_avg_npc_042.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_002_amiya_1#5","name2":"avg_npc_042","focus":"1","id":318},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿米娅","text":"啊，等等，迷迭香......我会摔倒的！","id":319,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/1/1a/Avg_char_002_amiya_5.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_002_amiya_1#5","name2":"avg_npc_042","focus":"2","id":320},{"type":"dialogue","name":"迷迭香","text":"我要抓紧点。不能让你被那些家伙，那些感染者，不能让他们伤到你。","id":321,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/6/6a/Avg_avg_npc_042.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_002_amiya_1#4","name2":"avg_npc_042","focus":"1","id":322},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿米娅","text":"慢点走......我们慢点走吧。","id":323,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/e/ed/Avg_char_002_amiya_4.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_012","id":324},{"type":"dialogue","name":"罗德岛干员","text":"......","id":325,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/1/1b/Avg_avg_npc_012.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"罗德岛干员","text":"（也许我不该那么说的。但......）","id":326,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/1/1b/Avg_avg_npc_012.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"罗德岛干员","text":"（嗯......）","id":327,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/1/1b/Avg_avg_npc_012.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":328},{"type":"character","id":329},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":330},{"type":"background","image":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/2/28/Avg_bg_bg_cherunder_2.png","screenadapt":"coverall","id":331},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":332},{"type":"text","text":"中央区","id":333},{"type":"dialog","id":334},{"type":"decision","options":{"1":{"id":"336","text":"你看见了吗，凯尔希？"}},"values":[],"id":335},{"type":"predicate","references":["1"],"id":336,"end":true},{"type":"dialog","id":337},{"type":"character","id":338},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"3","block":"true","id":339},{"type":"image","image":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/c/c8/Avg_avg_8_24.png","x":"0","y":"100","xScale":"1.2","yScale":"1.2","fadetime":"0","id":340},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","fadetime":"1.5","block":"false","id":341},{"type":"character","id":342},{"type":"imagetween","yFrom":"100","yTo":"0","xScaleFrom":"1.2","yScaleFrom":"1.2","xScaleTo":"1","yScaleTo":"1","duration":"15","block":"false","id":343},{"type":"dialogue","name":"牧群化萨卡兹战士","text":"呃，呃。","id":344},{"type":"dialogue","name":"牧群化萨卡兹战士","text":"别，别靠近。","id":345},{"type":"dialog","id":346},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":347},{"type":"image","fadetime":"0","id":348},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","fadetime":"0.6","block":"false","id":349},{"type":"character","name":"char_003_kalts_1","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":350},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":351},{"type":"dialogue","name":"凯尔希","text":"看见了。任何一个视力还正常的人都不能无视这种现象。","id":352,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/d/d3/Avg_char_003_kalts_1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"凯尔希","text":"——你还记得你在龙门遭遇的特殊感染者吗？","id":353,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/d/d3/Avg_char_003_kalts_1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"凯尔希","text":"那一个会促使其他感染者的器官发生变异的整合运动少年感染者。","id":354,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/d/d3/Avg_char_003_kalts_1.png"},{"type":"decision","options":{"1":{"id":"356","text":"谁？"},"2":{"id":"356","text":"......"},"3":{"id":"356","text":"我记得。"}},"values":[],"id":355},{"type":"predicate","references":["1","2","3"],"id":356,"end":378},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_091","id":357},{"type":"dialogue","name":"牧群化萨卡兹战士","text":"......啊。","id":358,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/f/f8/Avg_avg_npc_091.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_1002_nsabr_2","id":359},{"type":"dialogue","name":"整合运动感染者","text":"梅菲斯特的牧群吗？！","id":360,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/2/27/Avg_char_1002_nsabr_2.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"整合运动感染者","text":"怎么魔族也......","id":361,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/2/27/Avg_char_1002_nsabr_2.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_091","id":362},{"type":"dialogue","name":"牧群化萨卡兹战士","text":"不要，不要向前，再往里走了。","id":363,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/f/f8/Avg_avg_npc_091.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_1002_nsabr_2","id":364},{"type":"dialogue","name":"整合运动感染者","text":"你干什么......我们要在前面布防的！叛徒快打到这里来了！","id":365,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/2/27/Avg_char_1002_nsabr_2.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"整合运动感染者","text":"梅菲斯特这个家伙，又在想什么？我们绕过去，他们不会攻击我们的......","id":366,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/2/27/Avg_char_1002_nsabr_2.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_091","id":367},{"type":"dialogue","name":"牧群化萨卡兹战士","text":"只会，痛苦。","id":368,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/f/f8/Avg_avg_npc_091.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_1002_nsabr_2","id":369},{"type":"dialogue","name":"整合运动感染者","text":"等一下，等一下！你们干什么！！","id":370,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/2/27/Avg_char_1002_nsabr_2.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_091","id":371},{"type":"dialogue","name":"牧群化萨卡兹战士","text":"痛苦。","id":372,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/f/f8/Avg_avg_npc_091.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_1002_nsabr_2","id":373},{"type":"dialogue","name":"整合运动感染者","text":"松手！！松手！！！","id":374,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/2/27/Avg_char_1002_nsabr_2.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_003_kalts_1","id":375},{"type":"dialogue","name":"凯尔希","text":"......","id":376,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/d/d3/Avg_char_003_kalts_1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"凯尔希","text":"各小队成员，我们转移。保持隐蔽。","id":377,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/d/d3/Avg_char_003_kalts_1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"凯尔希","text":"接下来我们要更换入口。有些不好的事情已经发生了。","id":378,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/d/d3/Avg_char_003_kalts_1.png","end":true},{"type":"dialog","id":379},{"type":"blocker","fadetime":"3","block":"true","id":380},{"type":"image","id":381}],"characters":["整合运动感染者","迷迭香小队成员","迷迭香","萨卡兹雇佣兵","阿米娅","罗德岛干员","凯尔希","牧群化萨卡兹战士"]}